name: GasChameleon
description: GASC is a crypto asset developed by Bitci Borsa Teknoloji Anonim Limited on Bitcichain. GasChameleon (GASC) is a digital asset for car tuning enthusiasts.It also supports GASC holders for vehicle accessories, spare parts and special projects. GASC is designed to meet the needs of car enthusiasts, build community and promote car projects.
